So it's all right then
if I can fix it

827
00:44:16,560 --> 00:44:19,639
for you and I to fly together?

828
00:44:19,640 --> 00:44:21,679
Jack, that would be great.

829
00:44:21,680 --> 00:44:22,519
Teddy, I never

