00:44:22,520 --> 00:44:23,000
I know.

831
00:44:23,200 --> 00:44:24,560
I know.

832
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:31,959
I know that, Chuck.

833
00:44:31,960 --> 00:44:37,039
But if something happens to me,
you gotta care for Ethel Ann.

834
