846
00:45:13,040 --> 00:45:17,160
Both of which are pretty dangerous.

847
00:45:20,640 --> 00:45:21,400
Oh, hi.

848
00:45:21,640 --> 00:45:22,120
Jack.

849
00:45:22,360 --> 00:45:24,239
Maybe you were expecting Pete.

850
00:45:24,240 --> 00:45:25,400
No.

851
00:45:26,560 --> 00:45:28,919
I guess you haven't seen
each other for a while, huh?

852
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:30,679
Jeez, that music is loud!

853
00:45:30,680 --> 00:45:32,479
Yeah, it is.

854
00:45:32,480 --> 00:45:35,719
She's not going out any more,
not even to dad's grave.

855
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:38,439
She's drinking,
she's cutting everyone off.

856
00:45:38,440 --> 00:45:40,639
Well, you are, too.

857
00:45:40,640 --> 00:45:43,119
Pete misses you, you know.

858
00:45:43,120 --> 00:45:44,879
For God's sakes, Jack,
I like Peter,

859
