She's moved back in there?

866
00:46:04,600 --> 00:46:05,519
What do you mean, back?

867
00:46:05,520 --> 00:46:07,279
That was always my room.

868
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:09,839
They were always in the other one.

869
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:11,560
Jack?

870
00:46:14,800 --> 00:46:15,720
Look

871
00:46:17,520 --> 00:46:21,159
Answer the phone, Marie,
and give her these, please.

872
00:46:21,160 --> 00:46:22,799
I'll come back some other time.

873
00:46:22,800 --> 00:46:23,560
Jack?

874
00:46:24,720 --> 00:46:25,480
Jack

875
00:46:32,960 --> 00:46:34,120
Hello?

876
00:46:34,440 --> 00:46:37,159
Is that America?

877
00:46:37,160 --> 00:46:38,639
Is this ajoke?

878
00:46:38,640 --> 00:46:39,880
No, wait.

879
00:46:40,960 --> 00:46:42,879
